OL,3,C'Dubious' if all-island court would
OL,4,Cconvict more fugitives ` Irish AG in
OL,5,C1982
OL,7,FIt was "rather dubious" whether an all-
OL,8,Fisland court would lead to the
OL,9,Fconviction of more fugitives,
OL,10,Faccording to Ireland's attorney
OL,11,Fgeneral in 1982.
OL,13,FPatrick Connolly SC, who would resign
OL,14,Flater that year after prolific
OL,15,Fmurderer Malcolm McArthur was arrested
OL,16,Fin his apartment, made his assessment
OL,17,Fshortly after the new Irish government
OL,18,Fwas formed.
