OL,7,FThe suggestion of a joint British-
OL,8,FIrish court was discussed during the
OL,9,F1980s.
OL,11,FA meeting was held in April 1982, a
OL,12,Fmonth after Charles Haughey came to
OL,13,Fpower for a second time and before his
OL,14,Fgovernment collapsed in December of
OL,15,Fthat year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
