OL,3,C'Dubious' if all-island court would
OL,4,Cconvict more fugitives ` Irish AG in
OL,5,C1982
OL,7,FMr Haughey, Mr Connolly, the minister
OL,8,Ffor foreign affairs Gerry Collins,
OL,9,Fminister for justice Sean Doherty, and
OL,10,Fsenior civil servants at several
OL,11,Fdepartments met to discuss matters
OL,12,Frelating to Northern Ireland.
OL,14,FIn a document labelled "strictly
OL,15,Fconfidential", released this year as
OL,16,Fpart of the National Archives in
OL,17,FDublin, Mr Connolly told the new Irish
OL,18,Fgovernment that he was against the
OL,19,Fsuggestion of an all-island court.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
