OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F305A1766897199
OL,3,C'Dubious' if all-island court would
OL,4,Cconvict more fugitives ` Irish AG in
OL,5,C1982
OL,7,FMr Connolly, who was thrown into the
OL,8,Fspotlight in August after Malcolm
OL,9,FMcArthur was arrested in his Dublin
OL,10,Fapartment, said he did not believe the
OL,11,Fcourt would lead to the conviction of
OL,12,Fmore fugitives.
OL,14,FHe recounted a meeting his predecessor
OL,15,Fhad with the British attorney general
OL,16,Fabout extradition, joint interrogation
OL,17,Fand an "all-island court" and then
OL,18,Fgave his view, according to the memo.
OL,26,@yD@HOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
