OL,7,FIn relation to joint interrogation, he
OL,8,Fsaid that gardai feared attacks would
OL,9,Fbe mounted at Garda stations if RUC
OL,10,Fofficers could be present and Mr
OL,11,FHaughey said that extradition was an
OL,12,F"explosive issue".
OL,14,FIn January of that year, before the
OL,15,Fgeneral election was called, a meeting
OL,16,Fwas held at Iveagh House attended by
OL,17,Ftaoiseach Garret FitzGerald, the
OL,18,Fministers for justice and foreign
OL,19,Faffairs, and then attorney general
OL,20,FPeter Sutherland SC.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@QO]
