OL,3,C'Dubious' if all-island court would
OL,4,Cconvict more fugitives ` Irish AG in
OL,5,C1982
OL,7,F"Questions arose about such a court's
OL,8,Fjurisdiction and rules of procedure,"
OL,9,Fthe note stated.
OL,11,F"There seemed to be agreement that the
OL,12,Fcourt could sit in the north and the
OL,13,Fsouth as necessary.
OL,15,F"If a case were initiated in the
OL,16,Fnorth, the court would deal with it
OL,17,Funder UK law and procedures, even if
OL,18,Fit was necessary to sit in the south.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]sD@AOUwD@AOU
